Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: US attack on Libya
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xq16
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 20 Apr 1986
Britain is the only Western European country to back US air strikes against terrorism headquarters in Libya. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less